No correction for the influence of lower
energy neutrons (from scattering inside the sample
and accelerator target) on the cross section is
mentioned. This effect could possibly account for
the discrepancy e.g. in the  I-127 cross section
(this work 2.74 mb, several other authors about 1.1
mb). See e.g. Phys.Lett.39B,1972,625, Nuovo Cim.Lett.
Statistical error only is given.  But
